Articles.Content: I noticed that most of Raptor9's craft disappeared along with his craft catalog page only saying [withdrawn]. Can a moderator please tell me what happened?
Question moved to Kerbal Network since it's not about the game. As for the answer, you'd have to ask Raptor9. Sometimes people leave the community.

Well, it appears that he also removed most of his craft from KerbalX - but last I checked, a few were left that he must have forgotten to remove. Think his YT is gone too. No idea what happened though.

I just looked myself...ALL his crafts are freaking GONE!!!

He was always a peppery fellow to deal with...communicating with...so who knows what happened

Damn Shame...such great crafts
